{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1e4fdb46bd","title":"关于叛徒问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bb108204f4","index":0,"year":1967,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"efe657a34a","type":"paragraph","text":"关于干部间题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"34da150102","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年六月）","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"38078d58b4","type":"paragraph","text":"我们这些干部都是经过长期炼的，还是要有人站出来，现在的情况是站出来就打。我们的事情是要人挂帅的，红卫兵能挂帅吗？今天上台，明天就可能被打倒，原因是他们政治上不成熟。现在我们要做很多工作，使那些主要干部站出来，哪怕是黎元洪式的人物也是好的，出来两年也行。红卫兵不行，没有经过炼，这样的大事情，信不过他们。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"ee3ef409a6","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"691ae23c4b","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"b3a9900eb9","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"f41006546d","type":"paragraph","text":"要爱护干部，要支持革命领导干部出来，革命小将现在叫他们挂帅还不行，有个培养的过程，但小将是可爱的，是无产阶级革命事业的接班人。","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"1a23616596","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"a0c33a6818","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"076730ddb9","type":"paragraph","text":"X全国应该有更多的第一把手站出来。","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"66e02258fa","type":"paragraph","text":"有了就改","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"1ff0cfed29","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年六月）","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"586ca51285","type":"paragraph","text":"如果有了错误定要痛痛快快承认错误，改正错误，改的越快、越彻底越好。绝不能扭扭担，香吞吐吐，更不能坚持错误，越走越远。（转引自六月二十七日河南军区检查报告）","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"a9a75804e6","type":"paragraph","text":"关于徒间题的指示","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"f3a566848e","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年六月）","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"31351b9034","type":"paragraph","text":"对于叛徒，除罪大恶极者外，在其不继续反共的条件下，予以自新出路。如能同头革命，还可以接待，但不能重新人党。","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"013acbf832","type":"paragraph","text":"关于对外宣传的指示","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"defc4a5c0e","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年六月十八日）","index":17,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"d06fe3e513","type":"paragraph","text":"有些外国人对我们《北京周报》、新华社的对外宣传有意见。宣传毛泽东思想发展了思克思主义，过去不搞，现在文化大革命以后大搞特搞，吹得太厉害，人家也接受不了。有些酷何必要自己来说，我们要谦虚，特别是对外，出去要谦康一点，当然就不要失掉原则。昨天氢弹公报，我就把“伟大的导师、伟大的领袖、伟大的统帅、伟大的手”统统勾掉了。“万分喜和激动的心情”我把“万分”也勾掉了。不是十分，也不是百分，也不是千分，而是万分，我一分也不要，统统勾掉了。","index":18,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"},{"id":"ec83423552","type":"paragraph","text":"·315","index":19,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd"}],"page":{"id":"ca27615e0a","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"1e4fdb46bd","start":328,"end":328}}}},"__N_SSG":true}